    {
      "id": "1b14750c-f3ba-807e-987d-fac575206891",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Results show that users are receptive to the dynaimic group formation feature of the ITS as users report to be satisfied with the system’s flexibility, adaptatibility and interactivity.",
